## ChatGPT widgets (`mcp-server/widgets/`)

Self-contained HTML with `text/html;profile=mcp-app` MIME type:

| Widget file | Tool | UI |
|-------------|------|-----|
| `itinerary.html` | `plan_trip` | Day blocks, confidence/score pills |
| `park-details.html` | `get_park_details` | Hero, weather, alerts, activities |
| `compare.html` | `compare_parks` | Side-by-side table |
| `park-list.html` | `search_parks` | Results grid |
| `events.html` | `find_events` | Event list |

Build/preview: `python scripts/generate_previews.py`, `scripts/build_widgets.py`  
Verify: `python scripts/test_local.py`, `scripts/deep_verify.py`, `scripts/verify_widgets.py`

