## Marketing pages (Next.js)

### `/chatgpt` — ChatGPT App Directory landing

- **File**: `next-frontend/src/app/chatgpt/page.jsx`
- **SEO**: indexable; canonical `/chatgpt`
- **CTA**: `NEXT_PUBLIC_CHATGPT_APP_URL` or default Apps Directory deep link
- **Content**: 6 capability cards (Plan, Park Details, Compare, Search, Events, Multi-turn), example prompts, install steps
- **Audience**: End users installing from [chatgpt.com/apps](https://chatgpt.com/apps)

### `/mcp` — Claude MCP connector landing

- **File**: `next-frontend/src/app/mcp/page.jsx`
- **SEO**: indexable; canonical `/mcp`
- **Connector URL**: `https://trailverse-mcp.onrender.com/mcp` (constant `MCP_URL` in page)
- **Content**: Same 6 tools, "Install in Claude" instructions, developer mode / custom connector steps
- **Audience**: Claude Desktop and claude.ai MCP users

Both pages link back to `nationalparksexplorerusa.com` for unlimited Trailie access.

