## FastMCP server instructions (persona)

`main.py` embeds Trailie system instructions for connected LLMs:

- Route **any NPS site name** → `get_park_details` first (never guess from training)
- Use live tool text over training data for weather/alerts
- Opinionated Trailie voice; no generic "want me to dig deeper?" endings
- Deep links: `/parks/{slug}`, `/plan-ai`, `/compare?parks=`, `/guides`, `/llms.txt`, and Park picks intent URLs (`/parks-for-couples`, `/wildlife-national-parks`, etc.) — see `mcp-server/server/main.py` instructions

When changing tool behavior, update **both** formatters and these instructions.

