## Voice vs MCP (do not confuse)

| Feature | Technology | Entry |
|---------|------------|-------|
| **Trailie Voice** | OpenAI Realtime API + WebRTC, 4 function tools | Website `VoiceButton` |
| **MCP / ChatGPT** | FastMCP, 5 tools, HTML widgets | Render MCP server |

Voice does **not** use MCP protocol. Documented in `mcp-server/README.md` second half.

