## Change checklist (MCP / ChatGPT work)

When modifying park or AI APIs:

1. Update Express route/controller
2. Update `mcp-server/server/client.py` method if path changed
3. Update `formatters.py` for `structuredContent` + text shape
4. Run `python scripts/test_local.py`
5. Refresh ChatGPT connector / Claude MCP after deploy
6. Update `/chatgpt` or `/mcp` marketing copy if user-facing capabilities changed
7. Confirm `MCP_BYPASS_KEY` still set on both Render services
